### ============================================================
### ORDERS — Create, List, Get, Cancel, Assign, Courier Actions
### Base URL: http://localhost:8000
### All endpoints require a valid JWT access token
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE
@courierToken = PASTE_COURIER_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CREATE ORDER (multipart/form-data — no JSON body)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Create Order — valid city and future delivery date
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city_id"

1
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="delivery_date"

2026-04-15T18:00:00
------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="description"

I need a birthday cake for my daughter — chocolate, 2kg, decorated with flowers
------FormBoundary--

###

### [SUCCESS] Create Order — no description (optional field)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary2

------FormBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city_id"

2
------FormBoundary2
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="delivery_date"

2026-05-01T10:00:00
------FormBoundary2--

###

### [FAIL — Security] Create Order — no auth token (401 Unauthorized)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary3

------FormBoundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city_id"

1
------FormBoundary3
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="delivery_date"

2026-04-15T18:00:00
------FormBoundary3--

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Create Order — invalid city_id (400 Invalid city ID)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary4

------FormBoundary4
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="city_id"

99999
------FormBoundary4
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="delivery_date"

2026-04-15T18:00:00
------FormBoundary4--


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# LIST MY ORDERS (requires JWT)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] List My Orders — default pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [SUCCESS] List My Orders — with pagination params
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/?skip=0&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] List My Orders — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/

###

### [FAIL — Validation] List My Orders — limit exceeds max (422)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/?limit=9999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# GET SPECIFIC ORDER (requires JWT)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Get Order — own order
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Get Order — access another user's order (403 Forbidden)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Get Order — non-existent order ID (404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-999999
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CANCEL ORDER (requires JWT — order creator only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Cancel Order — valid cancellation reason
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Changed my mind about the gift"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Cancel Order — different user tries to cancel (403)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Unauthorized cancel attempt"
}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Cancel Order — non-existent order (404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-000000/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Should fail"
}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Cancel Order — no token (401)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Anonymous cancel attempt"
}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# COURIER — GET AVAILABLE ORDERS (courier token required)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Courier Get Available Orders — approved courier
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/available
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Courier Available Orders — customer token used (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/available
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Courier Available Orders — no token (401)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/available


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# COURIER — ACCEPT ORDER
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Courier Accept Order — available courier accepts a NEW order
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100002/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Accept Order — customer tries to accept (403 Only couriers)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100002/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Not Found] Accept Order — order doesn't exist (404)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-999999/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# CONFIRM DELIVERY (customer confirms before courier completes)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Confirm Delivery — customer confirms their order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/confirm-delivery
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Confirm Delivery — courier tries to confirm customer's delivery (403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/confirm-delivery
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Confirm Delivery — no token (401)
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100001/confirm-delivery


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# COURIER — GET ACTIVE ORDERS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Courier Active Orders — courier's in-progress orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/active
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Courier Active Orders — customer token (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/active
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# COURIER — GET STATS
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Courier Stats — active count + today's earnings
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Courier Stats — non-courier user (403)
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/courier/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}


# ---------------------------------------------------------------
# UPDATE ORDER STATUS (courier only)
# ---------------------------------------------------------------

### [SUCCESS] Update Order Status — courier moves to in_progress
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100002/status?status=in_progress
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Validation] Update Order Status — invalid status value (400)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100002/status?status=hacked_status
Authorization: Bearer {{courierToken}}

###

### [FAIL — Security] Update Order Status — customer tries to update (403)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/orders/ORDR-100002/status?status=in_progress
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
